Class DJSONReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • DAL.DJSONReader
  • public class DJSONReader
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to pull data from a JSON File. Although it was created to get any info in JSON after a while it was specialised to obtain data from game.json file.
